<h2>The Challenge</h2>

<div class="side-by-side">
  <p class="big">{{ subtitle }}</p>
  <p>
    Staring at the Sun wanted a visual identity that extended beyond traditional
    album artwork—something that could evolve alongside their music, build an
    interactive narrative, and engage audiences across streaming platforms and
    social media. My role was to develop a cohesive 3D animated aesthetic that
    translated seamlessly across Spotify Canvas loops, animated music videos,
    and cryptic promotional content that would tease future releases.
  </p>
</div>

