  <p class="big">Crafting a Cinematic Visual Identity</p>
  <p>
    Sungazer's single artwork is a 3D rendering made entirely in Blender. We
    iterated on different motion designs for a Spotify canvas, including an
    animated version of the artwork. Our chosen direction emphasized the lore
    and worldbuilding we're developing for the project.
  </p>
</div>
